{"info":{"intro":"介绍:    一个消极怠工的古代庶女，生活如此艰难，何必卖力奋斗。古代贵族女子的人生基调是由家族决定的，还流行株连，一个飞来横祸就会彻底遭殃，要活好活顺活出尊严，明兰表示，鸭梨很大。古代太危险了，咱们还是睡死算了。\n","title":"知否？知否？应是绿肥红瘦","id":"38304","author":"关心则乱"},"chapters":[{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947876.html","title":"第1章","id":0},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947877.html","title":"第2章","id":1},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947878.html","title":"第3章","id":2},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947879.html","title":"第4章","id":3},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947880.html","title":"第5章","id":4},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947881.html","title":"第6章","id":5},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947882.html","title":"第7章","id":6},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947883.html","title":"第8章","id":7},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947884.html","title":"第9章","id":8},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947885.html","title":"第10章","id":9},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947886.html","title":"第11章","id":10},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947887.html","title":"第12章","id":11},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947888.html","title":"第13章","id":12},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947889.html","title":"第14章","id":13},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947890.html","title":"第15章","id":14},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947891.html","title":"第16章","id":15},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947892.html","title":"第17章","id":16},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947893.html","title":"第18章","id":17},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947894.html","title":"第19章","id":18},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/38/38304/13947895.html","title":"第20章","id":19}]}